turns.ai_line: Good morning doctor, I dey feel serious pain for my belle after I chop leftover rice wey don stay for house. I dey throw up and my belle dey run too. I dey live for area wey rain dey fall wella so food dey spoil quick quick. I no fit bear this pain again abeg.
Doctor, this pain na him wey I no fit understand. E dey come and go. Na so so sweat dey catch me. I don try use agbo but e no work. Wetin I fit do abeg?

Doctor, I need help o. The pain too much for me. I bin chop leftover rice yesterday night, e come be like say belle wan tear since then. I don dey purge and I even vomit sef. E dey worry me say na only me chop the rice for house, but na only me wey dey sick like this. You fit helep me check wetin the problem be?
